init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The mugs flash, and then go back to their original ranking.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I reach out and touch one of the mugs.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I grab it and look at the name on it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I dont want to be the father that takes his kid to a ballgame once in a while and calls it good.
